<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefbf97a1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s4818"><num value="4818">§ 4818.</num><heading> Administrative provision</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of this chapter applicable to orders shall be applicable to amendments to orders.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefbf97a2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/198/tXVI/s1629">Pub. L. 99–198, title XVI, § 1629</ref>, <date date="1985-12-23">Dec. 23, 1985</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/99/1621">99 Stat. 1621</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
