<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="idefbf97a4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="idefbf97a5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section effective <date date="1986-01-01">Jan. 1, 1986</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/99/198/s1631">section 1631 of Pub. L. 99–198</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s4801">section 4801 of this title</ref>.</p>
